# Canonical source

Test gates per phase: [docs/roadmap.md](../../docs/roadmap.md). Bid tests required in Phase 3a before WebSockets.

- Critical business flows must have tests.
- Test edge cases.
- Test authorization flows.
- Test transactional consistency.
- Avoid brittle tests.
- Prefer integration and feature tests for business flows.
- Mock external services appropriately.